name: Mi Amour - Earrings
description: Round raw brass charms that say "AMOUR" sit in the middle of flat circular rings made of tiger ebony. Added to the front of the earrings are coral colored lilies. Earrings dangle from 14K gold-filled earring hooks. They measure 2.5 inches long from the top of the earring hooks to the bottom of the rings.

name: Spring Blossoms - Necklace (Portion of Sale to Go to the DementiaCare Foundation)
description:
From the Faith and Hope Line comes this necklace. This necklace features a gold batik vermeil pendant with a print of songbirds perched on cherry blossoms. The pendant hangs from a sterling silver chain. Pendant measures 1.5 inches and the necklace is 18 inches around. It is finished with a sterling silver spring ring clasp.

50% of sales from this necklace will go to the DementiaCare Foundation. Contact me if you have any questions.

name: My Indecisiveness - Earrings
description: Indecisive? Me too! Give a little glam to your indecisiveness with these absolutely gorgeous earrings. One earring is made of a brass coin with the word "non" on it. The other earring is made of the same brass coin, but this time the word "oui" is present. At the top of each coin is a vintage coral lily (made of plastic). Earrings are finished with 14K gold-filled earring hooks. They measure 1.75 inches from top of hook to bottom of earring.

name: Kiss My You Fool - Earrings
description: These incredibly lightweight earrings are adorable, fun and add a little something to just about any outfit. Brass boy and girl kissing charms dangle from each earring. One side has a round "LOVE" charm and the other side has a matching round charm, this time with the word "AMOUR". Each are raw brass. Peach colored roses add color to the whole ensemble. Earrings are finished with gold-filled earring hooks. The longer earring measure 4 inches from the very top of the earring hook to the bottom of the earring. The shorter earring measures 3.5 inches.

name: Bird in Flight Necklace
description: A beautiful sterling silver Swallow pendant suspends from sterling silver chain to form this necklace. The chain is a scored cable chain, with large oval links combined with smaller links. Necklace measures approximately 18" around, and is finished with a sterling silver springring clasp.
